      <title>沙特将以 33 亿英镑新交易收购希思罗机场更多股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ardian-saudi-fund-offer-to-buy-38-of-heathrow-for-3-3-billion</link>
